{
  "name": "Divider",
  "tier": "02_components",
  "key": "divider",
  "type": "atom",
  "description": "A horizontal line component for visually separating content areas.",
  "guidelines": {
    "purpose": "Divider is a horizontal line component for visually separating content areas. It clearly isolates information groups within list items, sections, cards, etc.",
    "anatomy": [
      "Divider line: var(--border-width-100), var(--color-border-tertiary)"
    ],
    "style": {
      "thickness": "var(--border-width-100)",
      "color": "var(--color-border-tertiary)"
    },
    "usage_guidelines": [
      "Used for visually indicating content separation. Not for decorative purposes.",
      "Divider occupies the full width of its container horizontally. Control the width via the parent container.",
      "Use in locations where content grouping is needed, such as lists, cards, and section delimiters."
    ],
    "do_dont": {
      "do": [
        "Place Divider between content groups."
      ],
      "dont": [
        "Do not use multiple Dividers consecutively for decorative purposes."
      ]
    },
    "_rawHtml": "\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Guide</h2>\n        <div class=\"guide-card\">\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Purpose</h3>\n            <p>Dividerは、コンテンツ領域を視覚的に区切るための水平線コンポーネントです。リストアイテム、セクション、カード内などで情報のグループを明確に分離します。</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Anatomy</h3>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--spacing-400);padding:var(--spacing-500) 0;max-width:calc(var(--sizing-100) * 100);\">\n              <div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;\">\n                <p style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-primary);padding:var(--spacing-300) 0;margin:0;\">Content area</p>\n                <div class=\"divider\" style=\"outline:var(--border-width-200) dashed var(--color-gradient-border-secondary-stop-1);outline-offset:var(--border-width-200);\"></div>\n                <p style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-primary);padding:var(--spacing-300) 0;margin:0;\">Content area</p>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color:var(--color-content-tertiary);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--spacing-200);\">\n                <span style=\"width:var(--sizing-300);height:var(--border-width-200);background:var(--color-gradient-content-stop-1);display:inline-block;border-radius:var(--border-width-100);\"></span>\n                Divider line — var(--border-width-100), <code style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;background: var(--color-background-secondary);padding:var(--border-width-100) var(--space-xxs);border-radius:var(--border-width-300);\">var(--color-border-tertiary)</code>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Style</h3>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-500);flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:var(--spacing-200);\">\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:var(--spacing-200);\">\n                <div style=\"width:calc(var(--sizing-100) * 50);height:var(--border-width-100);background:var(--color-border-tertiary);\"></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-tertiary);\">Thickness: var(--border-width-100)</span>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:var(--spacing-200);\">\n                <div style=\"width:var(--sizing-800);height:var(--sizing-400);border-radius:var(--border-width-300);background:var(--color-border-tertiary);\"></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-tertiary);\">Color: var(--color-border-tertiary)</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Usage Guidelines</h3>\n            <ul class=\"guide-list\">\n              <li>コンテンツの区切りを視覚的に示す目的で使用します。装飾的な目的には使用しません。</li>\n              <li>Dividerは水平方向にコンテナの全幅を占めます。幅の調整は親コンテナ側でコントロールしてください。</li>\n              <li>リスト、カード、セクション区切りなど、コンテンツのグルーピングが必要な場所で使用します。</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Do &amp; Don't</h3>\n            <div class=\"do-dont-grid\">\n              <div class=\"do-card\">\n                <div class=\"do-card-header do\">✓ Do</div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-body\">\n                  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;width:100%;border:var(--border-width-100) solid var(--color-border-tertiary);border-radius:var(--border-radius-200);overflow:hidden;background: var(--color-background-white);\">\n                    <div style=\"padding:var(--space-lg) var(--spacing-300);font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-primary);\">Section A</div>\n                    <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n                    <div style=\"padding:var(--space-lg) var(--spacing-300);font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-primary);\">Section B</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-desc\">コンテンツグループ間にDividerを置く。</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"do-card\">\n                <div class=\"do-card-header dont\">✕ Don't</div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-body\" style=\"opacity:0.6;\">\n                  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;width:100%;gap:var(--spacing-100);\">\n                    <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-desc\">装飾目的で複数のDividerを連続使用しない。</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n    "
  },
  "selector": ".divider"
}